Mac Brown (Brown-Forman): Family Business

J. McCauley “Mac” Brown, Vice President of Brown-Forman Corporation, discusses his children, his wife Eileen, and his parents Robinson and Jean McCauley Brown. This interview is from the Kentucky Bourbon Tales Oral History Project, Louie B. Nunn Center for Oral History, University of Kentucky Libraries. Watch the full interview: http://www.kentuckyoralhistory.org/interviews/27849. Share
