 Who We Are 


  ProfileFor more than 37 years, MacB has been solving some of the Nation’s most complex National Security challenges by offering advanced engineering services, cybersecurity and product solutions.
  History and TimelineWith a foundation built on meeting and exceeding the ever-changing National Security challenges, MacB has stayed true to company principles during its 37-year history of putting our Nation first.
  Message from the CEOPresident and CEO, Sid Fuchs, leads a team of more than 1,500 employees worldwide who are focused on strategic growth, and maintaining a collaborative culture dedicated to exceeding expectations.
  Leadership TeamMacB’s Senior Leadership Team works together across multiple disciplines to support customers, grow the strategic needs of the company and meet the needs of dedicated employees.
  Board of AdvisorsThese highly-regarded members of MacB’s Board of Advisors ensure that we continue to meet the current and future needs of our valued customers.
  Community InvolvementCommunity service, fundraising, gift drives and charity donations are all engrained into the MacB culture - with employees committed to giving back to local and national organizations.
  Office LocationsWith 17 offices in the U.S., we work closely with valued customers to increase capabilities and support mission success.
  AwardsThroughout our 37-year history, MacB has been awarded dozens of customer, innovation, product and workplace awards.
  CertificationsOur Integrated Standards Model highlights MacB's leadership in innovation, achieving differentiation among competitors and creating a culture of continual improvement. 
  Integrated LaboratoriesMacB has a consolidated set of R&D, test, and low rate production facilities to develop solutions across a broad base of customer mission areas.



 What We Do 


  Intelligence and AnalysisMacB provides a broad spectrum of technical and operational solutions to the Intelligence Community and the military 24 hours a day, seven days a week. Leaders depend on our technology solutions and analysis to make critical decisions. 
  CybersecurityMacB’s cyber solutions and services are designed to immediately identify, respond and neutralize cyber threats, and exploit vulnerabilities in target environments.
  Secure Cloud Eng/Data AnalyticsWe understand how critical it is to develop, deploy and sustain security-based systems that combat cyber threats, and support the entire complex system development life cycle. 
  RDT&EMacB is a leader in supporting RDT&E for multiple customers. Our R&D and test efforts span across all commodities from cyber, to sensors, to airborne platforms.
  Engineering and QRCTechnology Engineering is the heart of what we do, and it’s also our passion. Combined with our Quick Reaction Capability process, we are experts at delivering the right solution, at the right time. 
  Information TechnologyMacB is a leader in software development, system integration and sustainment of leading-edge IT services. We've adopted an Integrated Standards Model that includes ISO 9001, ISO 20000, and Level 3 CMMI certifications and best practices. 
  Logistics and Life Cycle MgmtWe have highly-trained logistics personnel and project managers with years of field experience working in support of program management, training and integration across the entire acquisition life cycle.
  Integrated LaboratoriesMacB has a consolidated set of R&D, test, and low rate production facilities to develop solutions across a broad base of customer mission areas.
  



 Who We Serve 


  A Pledge of Excellence“Commitment to Excellence” is our guiding philosophy and governs everything we do at MacB.
  Department of DefenseProviding the men and women that faithfully serve our country with the best technology and engineering solutions has been our guiding principle for more than 37 years. 
  Intelligence CommunityMacB provides innovative and cost-effective Intelligence, Cybersecurity, and Engineering solutions and services that keep our Nation safe.
  Special Operations For more than 25 years, the Special Operations Forces community has relied on MacB's innovative and proven engineering services and solutions to execute dynamic mission requirements. 
  Homeland SecurityWe have more than 20 years of experience delivering dynamic engineering services and product solutions in a quick-reaction capability environment.
  Federal AgenciesMacB delivers essential engineering, Information Technology and programmatic products and services for a wide range of federal agencies.



