Who We Are 
MacAulay-Brown, Inc. (MacB) provides advanced engineering, cybersecurity and product solutions to the Department of Defense (DoD), Intelligence Community (IC), Special Operations Forces (SOF), Department of Homeland Security (DHS) and Federal Agencies.
With Corporate Headquarters in Dayton, Ohio and National Capital Headquarters in Vienna, Virginia, MacB has more than 1,500 employees worldwide who are dedicated to developing mission-focused and results-oriented solutions that make a difference where and when it matters most. 

Learn More


What We Do 
For more than 37 years, MacB has been solving some of the Nation’s most complex National Security challenges. We are committed to delivering mission-critical capabilities in the areas of Intelligence and Analysis, Cybersecurity, Secure Cloud Engineering, Research and Development, Integrated Laboratories,  Information Technology and Life Cycle Management.

Learn More 


